  "texts": [
    "Using one-tailed logistic regression analyses did not lead 10.3389/frobt.2023.1277635 to an underpowered study, as a minimum of 40 participants was required using the same G*Power settings.",
    "It is also important to note that although Gao et al. (2023) did not use a within-participants design (their participants were each exposed to half of the stimuli), our study did, with 20 stimuli.",
    "It would therefore be expected to achieve sufficient power, if not more, with fewer participants.",
    "Most of the participants in our study had a technical background.",
    "Students from different disciplines might be less capable of identifying an AI system."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Using one-tailed logistic regression analyses did not lead 10.3389/frobt.2023.1277635 to an underpowered study, as a minimum of 40 participants was required using the same G*Power settings.",
    "It is also important to note that although Gao et al. (2023) did not use a within-participants design (their participants were each exposed to half of the stimuli), our study did, with 20 stimuli."
